{
  "texts": [
    "The TCGA dataset was used to train and evaluate DeepSurvNet, which is built on the GoogLeNet 30 architecture.",
    "A private dataset was also used to generalize DeepSurvNet.",
    "In the testing phases, their model obtained precisions of 99% and 80%.",
    "They also examined the frequency of genes linked to each class.",
    "31 employed DCNN to predict the mutational status of isocitrate dehydrogenase (IDH), an essential biomarker in glioblastoma."
  ]
}